<i>Hamajlija.</i>

521
01:10:09,875 --> 01:10:10,875
¡Selma!

522
01:10:14,750 --> 01:10:15,750
¡Selma!

523
01:14:18,791 --> 01:14:20,625
Hazte a un lado, Alex.

524
01:14:24,083 --> 01:14:25,083
Mi amor,

525
01:14:26,000 --> 01:14:29,208
baja el arma.

526
01:14:31,625 --> 01:14:32,625
